.TH bilidownloader-history-clear 1 "November 2025" "bilidownloader 3.0.5" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
bilidownloader-history-clear - Clear history
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bilidownloader history clear
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Clear history. Alias: clean, purge, cls, del, rm
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--by-series, -s\fR TEXT
Clear history for a specific series (fuzzy match on title or exact match on ID).
.TP
\fB--by-date, -d\fR TEXT
Clear history older than specified date (YYYY-MM-DD format).
.TP
\fB--by-episode, -e\fR TEXT
Clear history for specific episode ID(s). Can be specified multiple times.
.TP
\fB--assumeyes, -y\fR
Automatically answer yes for all questions.
.TP
\fB--history, --history-file, -h\fR PATH
Path to your history.txt file (default: /home/nattadasu/Bilibili/history.v2.tsv).
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR bilidownloader-history (1),
